show.title: Blood Contract

show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/Hm2UMk
show.description: Rosy, a woman who has lost everything—her job, her direction, her purpose—crosses paths with Sam, a wealthy and enigmatic vampire. When he offers her an unusual proposition to become his contract bride, Rosy faces an impossible choice. Though terrified by the shadows of Sam's otherworldly existence, she accepts his offer, seeing it as her last chance at a meaningful life. As their arrangement unfolds, Rosy is drawn deeper into a realm of immortal desires and dangerous secrets, where the line between opportunity and oblivion grows increasingly thin.
